@@TJvComboListBox
<TITLEIMG TJvComboListBox>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.ListsAndTrees.Lists
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  A listbox that displays a combobox overlaying the selected item.
Description
  TJvComboListBox is an ownerdrawn listbox that displays a combobox overlaying the selected item.
  If you assign a TPopupMenu to the DropdownMenu property, the menu is displayed when the user 
  clicks on the combobox button. This component inherits from TJvCustomListBox and publishes many of 
  it's properties and events as well as adding new ones like DropdownMenu, DrawStyle, OnDrawImage and OnDrawText.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.AddImage
Summary
  Adds an image to the listbox.
Description
  Use AddImage to add a TPicture to the Items list. AddImage is a helper function that assures
  that the image is copied to an internal TPicture and added to the Items.Objects list. 
  You can also call Items.AddObject directly if you prefer.
Parameters
  P - The picture to add. A copy is created internally and added to the Items.Objects list.
Return value
  Returns the index of the item in the Items list.
See Also
  AddText, Delete, Items
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.AddText
Summary
  Adds a string to the listbox.
Description
  Use AddText to add a string to the Items list. AddText is a helper function and is equivalent
  to calling Items.Add.
Parameters
  S - The string to add.
Return value
  Returns the index of the item in the Items list.
See Also
  AddImage, Delete, Items
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.Delete
Summary
  Deletes an item from the Items list.
Description
  Delete is equivalent to Items.Delete but also makes sure that if the item delted contains a TPicture, the
  picture is freed.
Parameters
  Index - \Index of the item to delete.
See Also
  AddImage, AddText, Items
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.DrawStyle
Summary
  Determines how images are drawn in the listbox.
Description
  Use DrawStyle to specify how images are drawn in the listbox. 
See Also
  TJvComboListBoxDrawStyle
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.DropdownMenu
Summary
  Determines the popupmenu to display when the user clicks the combobox button.
Description
  Assign a TPopupMenu to the DropdownMenu to display it when the user clicks the combobox button in the listbox.
  DropdownMenu is separate from PopupMenu but can point to the same TPopupMenu if necessary.
See Also
  PopupMenu
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.OnDrawImage
Summary
  Occurs when an image is about to be drawn in the list.
Description
  Write a handler for this event when you want to take specific actions when an image is about to be drawn.
Parameters
  Sender      - The component that called the event.
  Index       - The index of the item in the Items list.
  APicture    - The image that is about to be drawn
  R           - The TRect of where the image is to be drawn.
  DefaultDraw - Set this to false to prevent the component to draw the image.
See Also
  OnDrawText
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.OnDrawText
Summary
  Occurs when a string is about to be drawn.
Description
  Write a handler for this event when you want to take specific actions when a string is about to be drawn.
Parameters
  Sender      - The component that called the event.
  Index       - The index of the item in the Items list.
  AText       - The text to draw.
  R           - The TRect of where the image is to be drawn.
  DefaultDraw - Set this to false to prevent the component to draw the text.
See Also
  OnDrawImage
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBoxDrawStyle
<TITLE TJvComboListBoxDrawStyle type>
Summary
  Defines the possible ways an image can be drawn in a TJvComboListBox.
Description
  TJvComboListBoxDrawStyle defines the possible ways an image can be drawn in a TJvComboListBox. This propety does not affect items
  that contains text.
@@TJvComboListBoxDrawStyle.dsOriginal
  Draw the image at original size. The image is clipped to the size of the drawing area. If the image is smaller than the display
  rect, it is centered accordingly.
@@TJvComboListBoxDrawStyle.dsStretch
  The image is stretched to fill the entire drawing area.
@@TJvComboListBoxDrawStyle.dsProportional
  The image is sized proportionally to the display area and centered.
